  <bodyText><![CDATA[<h2>Italy by Train 2024 / 2025</h2>
<p>Travel to Italy by train and track a path through its mesmerising landscapes. Every carriage is a window seat to Italy's picturesque beauty. </p>
<div class="c-tabs-beta__content-table--row-wrapper">
<p><img src="/media/13100434/bellagio_ferry_point.jpg" alt="italy by train" data-udi="umb://media/af1a6176bdd34f258f59f21597ca1334" /></p>
<h3>Italy Holidays by Train</h3>
<p><span>All aboard for a simpler journey! Leave behind airport hassles and enjoy the comfort and views of train travel. Arrive directly at your destination, relaxed and ready to explore.</span></p>
<p>Book online by selecting 'London St Pancras' for departure or <a data-udi="umb://document/e5b8abf94a554299a3960566b88e9193" href="/{localLink:umb://document/e5b8abf94a554299a3960566b88e9193}" title="Contact Us">contact us</a> to find out more. </p>
